===賽前===
[[File:Jules_Bianchi_Bahreïn_2014.jpg|thumb]]於比賽前一周的[[2014年日本大獎賽|日本大獎賽]]發生事故後，[[瑪魯西亞車隊|瑪魯西亞車隊]]僅派出[[馬克斯·齊爾頓|馬克斯·齊爾頓]]一輛{{le|瑪魯西亞MR03|Marussia MR03|MR03}}，照片攝於[[2014年巴林大獎賽|巴林大獎賽]]。<ref name="marussia 1 car"/>]]
====瑪魯西亞參賽車手====
[[瑪魯西亞車隊|瑪魯西亞]]車手[[儒勒·比安奇|儒勒·比安奇]]在[[2014年日本大獎賽|日本大獎賽]]出示黃旗時，撞上一輛正在處理[[艾德里安·蘇蒂爾|艾德里安·蘇蒂爾]]的[[薩伯車隊|薩伯]]的拖拉機，遭遇了嚴重的頭部損傷，使他無法參賽俄羅斯大獎賽。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www1.skysports.com/f1/report/28593/9504602/jules-bianchi-undergoes-surgery-in-hospital-after-suffering-severe-head-injuries|title=Jules Bianchi undergoes surgery in hospital after suffering 'severe' head injuries|work=[[Sky_Sports_F1|skysportsf1.com]]|publisher=[[BSkyB|BSkyB]]|date=2014-10-05|accessdate=2014-10-06|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006092549/http://www1.skysports.com/f1/report/28593/9504602/jules-bianchi-undergoes-surgery-in-hospital-after-suffering-severe-head-injuries|dead-url=no}}</ref>車隊根據國際汽聯的規定派出兩輛車，另一位是他們指派來頂替比安奇出賽這場賽事的測試及儲備車手[[亞歷山大·羅西_(賽車手)|亞歷山大·羅西]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/09/rossi-nominated-stand-bianchi-marussia/|title=Rossi nominated to stand in for Bianchi at Marussia|first=Keith|last=Collantine|publisher=Keith Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|date=2014-10-09|accessdate=2014-10-10|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721145132/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/09/rossi-nominated-stand-bianchi-marussia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過車隊在周五練習賽前獲得國際汽聯的批准，決定讓[[馬克斯·齊爾頓|馬克斯·齊爾頓]]作為他們的唯一代表，不發出第二輛車，最終在發車位上總共有21輛車。車隊仍在整個比賽周末將比安奇的賽車放置於他的車庫，並將他的制服掛在牆上，以表示對他與他的家人的尊重。<ref name="marussia 1 car">{{cite news|url = http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/116245|title = Marussia enters one car for Chilton after Bianchi crash|last = Noble|first = Jonathan|date = 2014-10-10|work = Autosport.com|accessdate = 2014-10-10|publisher = Haymarket Publications|archive-date = 2015-06-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150626145614/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/116245|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Marussia to run a single car in Russia out of respect for Bianchi|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/10/marussia-run-single-car-russia-respect-bianchi/|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-10-10|accessdate=2014-10-10|archive-date=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150721145013/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/10/marussia-run-single-car-russia-respect-bianchi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
