====處罰====
[[帕斯托·馬爾多納多|帕斯托·馬爾多納多]]因超出本季五組引擎的配額，在[[2014年日本大獎賽|日本大獎賽]]受到十位罰退。<ref name="MAL pen">{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/03/maldonado-set-ten-place-grid-penalty/|title=Maldonado set for ten-place grid penalty|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-10-03|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-date=2015-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150816070503/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/03/maldonado-set-ten-place-grid-penalty/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，因為他的排位為第17位，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/931/7406/ |title=2014 Japanese Grand Prix — Qualifying Results |work=Formula1.com |publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]] |date=2014-10-04 |accessdate=2014-10-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006030500/http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/931/7406/ |archivedate=2014-10-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/04/2014-japanese-grand-prix-grid/|title=2014 Japanese Grand Prix grid|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-10-04|accessdate=2014-10-04|archive-date=2015-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150816231800/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/04/2014-japanese-grand-prix-grid/|dead-url=no}}</ref>因此他並無法採取完整的懲罰，若是如此他將會超出發車位上的22位及最後一位。在[[2014年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2014年賽季]]的新規則下，<ref name="further changes">{{cite news|title=Further rule changes confirmed for 2014|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.UK/2013/12/12/2014-f1-rules-more-changes/|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706025132/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2013/12/12/2014-f1-rules-more-changes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>懲罰的剩餘部分將會移轉至俄羅斯大獎賽，也就是將自動罰退他五位。<ref name="MAL HUL">{{cite news|title=Grid drops for Hulkenberg and Maldonado|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/10/grid-drops-hulkenberg-maldonado/|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-10-10|accessdate=2014-10-11|archive-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509211628/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/10/grid-drops-hulkenberg-maldonado/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
====輪胎====
[[一級方程式輪胎|輪胎]]供應商[[倍耐力|倍耐力]]宣布他們將提供各隊白色中性胎作為較硬的首選胎，以及黃色軟胎作為備選胎，以應付全新的賽道表面以及承受輪胎所受的高側向載荷，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/09/11/pirelli-selects-tyres-first-russian-grand-prix/|title=Pirelli selecrs tyres for first Russian Grand Prix|first=Keith|last=Collantine|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-09-11|accessdate=2014-09-12|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006173748/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/09/11/pirelli-selects-tyres-first-russian-grand-prix/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="200kph">{{cite news|title=Sochi uncovered — the inside track on Russia's first F1 circuit|url=http://www.formula1.com/news/features/2014/10/16469.html|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2014-10-09|accessdate=2014-10-10|archive-date=2015-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117174444/http://www.formula1.com/news/features/2014/10/16469.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>特別像是在4號彎，這是估計速度達到{{convert|200|kph|mph|abbr=off}}的一條細長半圓形彎角，也是今年一級方程式賽車賽曆中最長的一段彎道。<ref name="200kph"/>

====減少空氣阻力系統====
這條賽道共有兩塊[[減少空氣阻力系統|減少空氣阻力系統]]區域。第一個偵測區位在起跑線與1號彎間，啟動區則位於彎角的頂點處。第二個偵測區位於賽道的長直道前，啟動區在10與11號彎間並在13號彎前終止。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/08/two-independent-drs-zones-sochi/|title=Two independent DRS zones for Sochi|first=Keith|last=Collantine|work=F1 Fanatic|publisher=Keith Collantine|date=2014-10-08|accessdate=2014-10-09|archive-date=2015-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150820081039/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/10/08/two-independent-drs-zones-sochi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===自由練習賽===
[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯車隊]]的[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]於第一階段自由練習賽寫下最快圈速，隊友[[劉易斯·漢米爾頓|劉易斯·漢米爾頓]]以0.07秒之差屈居第二，之後是落後0.2秒的[[麥拉倫車隊|麥拉倫車隊]]車手[[詹森·巴頓|詹森·巴頓]]。<ref name="fp1 times">{{cite news|url=http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/930/7397/|title=2014 Formula 1 Russian Grand Prix — Free Practice 1 results|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2014-10-10|accessdate=2014-10-10|archive-date=2014-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010210307/http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/930/7397/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AFgp%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%B7%B4%E7%BF%92%E4%B8%80ro-rg%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB-084500972.html|title=俄羅斯GP自由練習一Rosberg最快|work=Racingnet|author=Chumiya|date=2014-10-10|accessdate=2014-10-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022045731/https://tw.sports.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AFgp%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E7%B7%B4%E7%BF%92%E4%B8%80ro-rg%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB-084500972.html|archivedate=2014-10-22}}</ref>另外，[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯車隊]]的[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]在設計用來將他的輪胎保持於最佳工作溫度的暖胎套失去作用後，損壞了他的輪胎，因此他僅做出有限的圈數。俄羅斯車手[[謝爾蓋·希洛金_(賽車手)|謝爾蓋·希洛金]]做出了他的一級方程式賽車處女秀，代替[[伊斯班·古鐵雷斯|伊斯班·古鐵雷斯]]為[[薩伯車隊|薩伯車隊]]出賽。<ref name="Sirotkin FP1">{{cite news|url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/09/10/sirotkin-make-f1-practice-debut-russia/|title=Sirotkin to make F1 practice debut in Russia|first=Keith|last=Collantine|date=2014-09-10|accessdate=2014-09-11|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723173255/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2014/09/10/sirotkin-make-f1-practice-debut-russia/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他最終排在第17位，比羅斯堡慢上2.5秒，在薩伯隊友[[艾德里安·蘇蒂爾|艾德里安·蘇蒂爾]]之後0.4秒。[[羅伯托·梅里|羅伯托·梅里]]也參與這次的練習賽，頂替[[卡特漢姆車隊|卡特漢姆車隊]]的[[小林可夢偉|小林可夢偉]]，這是他本季為該隊的第三次亮相。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.caterhamf1.com/news/2014/2014-russian-grand-prixview |title=2014 Russian Grand PrixView |work=caterhamf1.com |publisher=[[Caterham_F1|Caterham F1 Team]] |date=2014-10-08 |accessdate=2014-10-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014233918/http://www.caterhamf1.com/news/2014/2014-russian-grand-prixview |archivedate=2014-10-14 }}</ref>

梅賽德斯車隊在第二階段自由練習賽再度居於領先地位，比後方的[[凱文·馬格努森|凱文·馬格努森]]和[[法拉利車隊|法拉利車隊]]的[[費爾南多·阿隆索|費爾南多·阿隆索]]快上0.8秒。羅斯堡雖然在最後一圈犯了一個錯誤，無法將他的成績再往上推進，但他最終仍排在第4名。<ref>{{cite news|title=2014 Formula 1 Russian Grand Prix — Free Practice 2 results|url=http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/930/7398/|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2014-10-10|accessdate=2014-10-11|archive-date=2015-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150117091939/http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/930/7398/|dead-url=no}}</ref>漢米爾頓在第三階段自由練習賽再次成為最快的車手，比羅斯堡快上0.3秒，之後屈居第三的則是鮑達斯。<ref name="fp3 times">{{cite news|url=http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/930/7399/|title=2014 Formula 1 Russian Grand Prix — Free Practice 3 results|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|date=2014-10-11|accessdate=2014-10-11|archive-date=2014-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012062052/http://www.formula1.com/results/season/2014/930/7399/|dead-url=no}}</ref>許多車手在模擬排位賽圈時遇上了麻煩，最顯著的則是馬格努森，他壓過路緣石跑出賽道後損壞了懸吊；而漢米爾頓在倒數第二彎發生打滑，差點便撞上牆。[[帕斯托·馬爾多納多|帕斯托·馬爾多納多]]在他的[[動能回收系統|動能回收系統]]失效後，便無法做出圈速。在[[GP2系列賽|GP2]]和[[GP3系列賽|GP3系列賽]]墊場賽的練習與排位賽的幫助下，賽道狀況使車手的速度在排位賽前能較比賽周末剛開始時快上3.5秒。<ref name="fp1 times"/><ref name="fp3 times"/>

在第一天的賽事後，官方在這條賽道做了一些改變，包括於第2－3號彎處的緩衝區增設減速帶，以阻止車手刻意跑出賽道以較快的速度進入第4號彎。<ref name="changes">{{cite news|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/116282|title=Russian GP: Tweaks made to kerbs, pitlane speed limit changed|first=Jonathan|last=Noble|work=autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Publications|date=2014-10-11|accessdate=2014-10-11|archive-date=2014-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031062618/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/116282|dead-url=no}}</ref>維修道限速也從{{convert|80|kph|mph|abbr=off}}下修至{{convert|60|kph|mph|abbr=off}}，以解決對狹窄的維修站入口及彎角的擔憂。<ref name="changes"/>

